'''1912年牙买加飓风'''（{{lang-en|1912 Jamaica hurricane}}）是这年11月在[[牙买加|牙买加]]缓慢徘徊、降下瓢泼大雨并引发重大洪灾的一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[1912年大西洋飓风季|1912年大西洋飓风季]]的最强风暴，于11月11日清晨经西南[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的[[低气压|低气压区]]发展而成。气旋起初缓慢向西北移动，之后转向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]，于11月13日达到飓风强度。接下来风暴继续缓慢增强，但转向东北移动后强化速度有所加快。11月17日清晨，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时185公里的最高强度，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下已达三级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。风暴继续向东北偏北移动，于11月18日从牙买加[[内格里尔|内格里尔]]附近登陆。飓风上岸后不断减弱，之后又回到加勒比海，于11月20日在牙买加北侧弱化成热带风暴。气旋向西穿越加勒比海，最终于11月22日在[[大开曼|大开曼]]西南方向洋面逐渐消散。

牙买加降下暴雨，部分地区降雨量高达910毫米。该岛北部和东部多座桥梁严重受损，飓风产生的狂风将约四分之一的香蕉树摧毁，多地电报线路中断，铁轨也受到狂风暴雨的沉重打击。岛屿周边海域波涛汹涌，[[滨海萨凡纳|滨海萨凡纳]]几乎被完全摧毁，有42人丧生。牙买加西部约有100幢民宅被毁，5000套建筑受损或毁于一旦。整个牙买加约有100人遇难，损失数额约150万美元（1912年美元）。此外，气旋还在[[古巴|古巴]][[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]区域引发大面积洪灾，共夺走五条人命。

== 气象历史 ==
{{Storm path|1912 Atlantic hurricane 7 track.png}}
1912年11月10日，[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]以南的中[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]出现[[低气压|低气压区]]，这片低气压区便是1912年牙买加飓风的源头。虽然低气压区可能是由数天前穿越[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]的[[东风波|东风波]]催生，但由于缺乏东加勒比海的观测数据而无法确定。<ref name="Metadata">{{cite web | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | author = Christopher Landsea, et al. | date = 2014-04 | display-authors = etal | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161124024737/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | archivedate = 2016-11-24 }}</ref>11月11日清晨，系统内发展出闭合[[大气环流|环流]]，气象机构因此于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]早上6点将位于[[巴拿马|巴拿马]][[科隆省_(巴拿马)|科隆省]][[波尔托韦洛区|波尔托韦洛区]]卡西克（{{lang|en|Cacique}}）以北约180公里洋面的天气系统归类成热带风暴<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Specialists Division | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = Easy-to-Read HURDAT 1851-2009 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。这片海域的[[气压|气压]]也持续下降，证明有热带天气系统正在发展并聚拢<ref name="WFW">{{cite journal | author = Henry C. Frankenfield | title = Weather, Forecasts and Warnings | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 1912-11 | volume = 40 | issue = 11 | pages = 1747–1778 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1912)40<1747:WFAW>2.0.CO;2 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042930/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1747.pdf | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1747.pdf | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | publisher = American Meteorological Society | bibcode = 1912MWRv...40.1747F }}</ref>。气旋缓慢北上，强度起初一直偏弱，但还是经逐渐强化于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}11月13日下午18点在[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]以东达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准<ref name="HURDAT" />。此时风暴中心附近的船只测得992[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.3[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）气压值<ref name="WFW" />。

气旋成为飓风后继续缓慢强化，并在转向东北后加快增强速度。11月18日，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]185公里的最高强度，已属三级飓风标准。<ref name="HURDAT" />气象学界一度认为气旋的最高强度达到四级飓风标准，但经[[大西洋飓风再分析计划|重新分析]]后降为三级。风暴规模相对较小，于11月18日晚沿[[牙买加|牙买加]]西海岸[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。南内格里尔角（{{lang|en|South Negril Point}}）在飓风登陆时测得965毫巴（百帕，28.5英寸汞柱）气压，这也是文献记载中本场风暴的最低气压值。<ref name="Metadata" />虽然在陆地上行进的时间很短，但气旋登陆后依然急剧减弱，并且回到加勒比海后仍在继续快速弱化。11月20日，飓风在[[古巴|古巴]]以南洋面减弱成热带风暴。<ref name="HURDAT" />由于此时这片海域的地面观测数据模凌两可，不足以做出准确判断，气象机构起初认为风暴应该是逐渐北上穿过大西洋抵达[[纽芬兰与拉布拉多|纽芬兰与拉布拉多]]<ref name="WFW" />，但也可能登陆[[纽约州|纽约州]]。经过现代重新分析，气象学家认定气旋是向西经过加勒比海<ref name="Metadata" />，在此期间缓慢减弱，最终于11月22日在[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]北面逐渐消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 影响和善后 ==
尚在南加勒比海发展时，飓风的外围[[雨带|雨带]]就在牙买加[[圣托马斯区_(牙买加)|圣托马斯区]]、[[波特兰区|波特兰区]]、[[圣安德鲁区_(牙买加)|圣安德鲁区]]和[[圣玛丽区_(牙买加)|圣玛丽区]]产生极端降水。10月10至12日，当地降雨总量高达910毫米，引发大面积洪灾并导致多条道路受损。<ref name="JamaicaReport">{{cite journal | title = The Storms Of November In Jamaica, West Indies | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 1912-11 | volume = 40 | pages = 1756–1757 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115203/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1756b.pdf | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1912)40<1756b:TSONIJ>2.0.CO;2 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/040/mwr-040-11-1756b.pdf | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | publisher = American Meteorological Society | format = PDF | deadurl = no | bibcode = 1912MWRv...40R1756. | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>牙买加东部和北部有多座桥梁受到重创<ref name="Kingston">{{cite news | title = Banana Trees Injured | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | issue = 13310 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850330/1912_jamaica_hurricane/? | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | date = 1912-11-16 | location = Washington, D.C. | archive-date = 2019-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190609121117/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850330/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。雨带产生的狂风还将大量[[香蕉|香蕉]]植株刮倒<ref name="JamaicaReport" />，损失数量估计约占总量的四分之一<ref name="UnprecedentedRains">{{cite news | title = Unprecedented Rains Hurt Jamaican Fruits | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 101 | issue = 126 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850519/1912_jamaica_hurricane/? | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = San Francisco Chronicle | date = 1912-11-17 | location = San Francisco, California | archive-date = 2019-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190612002949/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850519/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>，[[联合果品公司|联合果品公司]]因此蒙受重大损失<ref name="Bananas">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Off Jamaican Coast | page = 3 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 78 | issue = 56 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850273/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = The Evening Observer | date = 1912-11-15 | location = Dunkirk, New York | archive-date = 2019-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190615020845/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850273/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>，多个香蕉种植园申报的损失高达60%<ref name="HurricaneCausesDamage">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Causes Damage | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/851081/1912_jamaica_hurricane/? | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | via = Newspapers.com | newspaper = The Leavenworth Times | date = 1912-11-19 | location = Leavenworth, Kansas | page = 1 | archive-date = 2019-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610130257/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/851081/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。1912年8月，当地香蕉产业还因另一场飓风经过受到严重破坏，11月的这场风暴更令灾情雪上加霜<ref>{{cite news | title = High Cost Of Bananas | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 21 | issue = 51 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/849979/august_1912_jamaica_hurricane/? | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | newspaper = the Kane Republican | date = 1912-11-12 | location = Kane, Pennsylvania | archive-date = 2019-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190606155826/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/849979/august_1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。岛上灾情随气旋逼近海岸线而进一步恶化，铁轨受到狂风暴雨的严重破坏，多条电报线路断裂，致使岛上通讯中断<ref name="StormContinues">{{cite news | title = Jamaican Storm Continues | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850390/1912_jamaican_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-22 | newspaper = The Parsons Daily Sun | date = 1912-11-18 | location = Parsons, Kansas | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 32 | issue = 325 | archive-date = 2019-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190606112407/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850390/1912_jamaican_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。

狂风和大浪导致许多树木连根拔起，多艘船只失事<ref name="JamaicaWrecked">{{cite news | title = Jamaica Swept By Storm; Many Boats Wrecked | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850620/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | newspaper = Fairbanks Daily Times | date = 1912-11-19 | location = Fairbanks, Alaska | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 9 | issue = 2158 | archive-date = 2019-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190615020843/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850620/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。[[滨海萨凡纳|滨海萨凡纳]]几乎被完全摧毁<ref name="EntireTown">{{cite news | title = Entire Town Wiped Out | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850669/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | newspaper = The Daily Northwestern | date = 1912-11-20 | location = Oshkosh, Wisconsin | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | agency = Associated Press | archive-date = 2016-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821062716/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/850669/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>，当地多所教堂受到重创。[[格林岛_(牙买加)|格林岛]]（{{lang|en|Green Island}}）、[[卢西|卢西]]和[[内格里尔|内格里尔]]也几乎被完全摧毁，其中内格里尔有一座教堂只剩部分房体依然屹立。[[蒙特哥贝|蒙特哥贝]]至少有300人流离失所，许多人家园毁于一旦后只能暂时寄住在当地法院，<ref name="tnya">{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6573706/the_new_york_age/ | page = 1 | date = 1912-12-05 | title = Jamaica Hard Hit By Hurricane | newspaper = New York Age | volume = 26 | issue = 10 | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2019-06-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190612023120/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/6573706/the_new_york_age/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>该市共有42人遇难<ref name="EntireTown" />。海岸沿线另有多个码头被狂风和大浪卷走<ref name="JamaicaScranton">{{cite news | title = Jamaica Hurricane | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/852123/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | newspaper = The Tribune-Republic | date = 1912-11-19 | location = Scranton, Pennsylvania | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | volume = 87 | issue = 44 | archive-date = 2019-06-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190611164037/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/852123/1912_jamaica_hurricane/ | dead-url = no }}{{Open access}}</ref>。牙买加西部约有100套民房被毁，另有约5000幢建筑受损或被毁<ref name="EntireTown" />。[[牙买加总督|牙买加总督]][[第一世奥利维尔男爵西德尼·奥利维尔|第一世奥利维尔男爵西德尼·奥利维尔]]（{{lang|en|Sydney Olivier, 1st Baron Olivier}}）亲自评估该岛西部灾情<ref name="tnya" />，英属牙买加政府下令出动300炮兵，把包括300顶帐篷在内的各种救灾物资送往灾区<ref name="EntireTown" />。此外，当地还筹资为无家可归者提供援助<ref name="tnya" />。

古巴主要是[[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]受到风暴影响，当地发生大面积洪灾，共有五人死亡，其中四人是遇溺的渔夫，另一人因房屋倒塌伤重不治<ref name="ency">{{cite book | author = David Longshore | title = Encyclopedia of Hurricanes, Typhoons, and Cyclones, New Edition | pages = 55-56 | location = New York | publisher = Facts on File | date = 2010-05-12 | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8kXwskQHBLoC&pg=PA56&lpg=PA56&dq=black+river+hurricane&source=bl&ots=qEJf5N9d-S&sig=3VRpXyvKHrEYPH17dwGF5d7Q3WI&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjw8YyGw4zNAhXBqh4KHc-BAQEQ6AEISjAL#v=onepage&q=black%20river%20hurricane&f=false}}</ref>。

